 - Recent notes and scribbled
                           phrases: <locus target="#2r">2r</locus>, 46v, 122ar, 179va.
 - Recent
                           notes and scribbled phrases: <locus target="#2r">2r</locus>, 46v, 122ar,
                           179va.</item>
